item.title: Jas Liu (劉傑思)
item.description: Hi, I’m Jas Liu! (Pronounced “jase”, rhymes with chase). My pronouns are they/them. I’m a Software Engineer at Radix Labs, where we build integrated automation solutions for biology labs. I currently lead front-end development for our Rainbow lab database and Timberland service controller, as well as general user authentication and navigation. Previously, I worked at the University of Chicago Energy & Environment Lab, where I developed predictive analytics models and data engineering processes for environmental policy research with the U.
